@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.exp(0.04))
    tmp = v0
    v2 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.40 + v1 + 0.52)) - ((v1 + 0.03 + v1 + 0.61) - (tmp + 0.06 / v1 + 0.51)))
    v1 = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.15 * tmp + 0.14) * v1))
    data[tid] = v0
